General.Name: TTA Holdings Ltd
General.Description: TTA Holdings Limited, together with its subsidiaries, distributes TEAC branded audio and visual consumer electronic products to retailers in Australia. Its products include televisions, soundbars, turntables, earbuds, headphones, Bluetooth speakers, and accessories comprising portable radio CD player, set top box, Bluetooth clock radio, USB conference microphone, and wireless charger. The company also offers its products online. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Thomastown, Australia. TTA Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of TT International Limited.
